<Algorithm code="           1. Let _thisMode_ be _F_.[[ThisMode]].           1. If _thisMode_ is ~lexical~, return ~unused~.           1. Let _calleeRealm_ be _F_.[[Realm]].           1. Let _localEnv_ be the LexicalEnvironment of _calleeContext_.           1. If _thisMode_ is ~strict~, then             1. Let _thisValue_ be _thisArgument_.           1. Else,             1. If _thisArgument_ is either *undefined* or *null*, then               1. Let _globalEnv_ be _calleeRealm_.[[GlobalEnv]].               1. Assert: _globalEnv_ is a Global Environment Record.               1. Let _thisValue_ be _globalEnv_.[[GlobalThisValue]].             1. Else,               1. Let _thisValue_ be ! ToObject(_thisArgument_).               1. NOTE: ToObject produces wrapper objects using _calleeRealm_.           1. Assert: _localEnv_ is a Function Environment Record.           1. Assert: The next step never returns an abrupt completion because _localEnv_.[[ThisBindingStatus]] is not ~initialized~.           1. Perform ! BindThisValue(_localEnv_, _thisValue_).           1. Return ~unused~.         ">
